### HTTP Request

`GET https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/loyalty/promos`

Returns list of all active promotions sorted by finish date (ascending).

| Parameter   | Type   | Required | Description                                                                  |
|-------------|--------|----------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| shop_id     | String | true     | Your API key                                                                 |
| shop_secret | String | true     | Your API secret key                                                          |
| stream      | String | false    | Stream to filter promos for different devices. Omit if you don't use streams |
